computing aesthetics. Measuring precisely 4cm across, this collectible piece features a pixel-perfect 8-bit globe rendered in vibrant shades of blue, green, and yellow, representing oceans, continents, and cloud cover with charming blocky simplicity. Suspended below the globe is a detailed control panel adorned with glowing buttons and indicators in bright cyan, magenta, and chartreuse – evoking the interface of a vintage system from the dawn of personal computing. The background’s deep black enhances the luminous colors, recreating the stark contrast of CRT monitors. Officially labeled \"WORIN CONTROL ROOM,\" this pin tells a silent story: a glimpse into the command center of an ancient global network, where early digital pioneers once managed systems with tangible, tactile controls. The enamel finish gives the pixels a smooth, polished depth, while the metal backing provides sturdy wearability. Perfect for collectors of retro tech, pixel art enthusiasts, or anyone who longs for the uncluttered digital magic of the 1980s. Wear your piece of computing history with pride. (Size: 4cm)","description_pl":"Wpatrz się w ekran tej ręcznie wykonanej, stylizowanej na retro konsoli kontroli planetarnej, stworzonej by rozpalić ducha wczesnej eksploracji kosmosu. Centralnym punktem jest kanciasta, pikselowa kula ziemska, prezentująca żywe, 8-bitowe kontynenty w oliwkowozieleni i chartreuse, kontrastujące z jasnoniebieskimi oceanami i niespodziewanymi plamami magenta. Poniżej czeka twoje dowodzenie: masywny panel sterowania, usiany dotykowymi, kwadratowymi przyciskami w elektrycznym błękicie, słonecznej żółci, głębokiej purpurze i mchowym zielonym, z centralnie umieszczonym, pojedynczym, wyrazistym żółtym pokrętłem. Na tle usianego gwiazdami czarnego pustki, rozproszone białe piksele imitują odległe konstelacje, a odważny pikselowy tekst „MAIN CONTROL ROOM” (GŁÓWNA SALA KONTROLI) zakotwicza scenę. To nie tylko wyświetlacz – to funkcjonalna kapsuła czasu, oddająca surową, optymistyczną estetykę sci-fi lat 80. i klasycznych gier komputerowych. Przekręć pokrętło, naciśnij przycisk i poczuj dreszcz emocji, będąc tym, który *naprawdę* kontroluje planety. Twój osobisty, kieszonkowy ośrodek dowodzenia czeka.","description_de":"","supplierName":"","supplierLink":"","priceComment":"","stock":0,"price":0,"sizeLength":0,"sizeWidth":0,"weight":0,"length":0,"parameters":[{"parameterId":"0a92f045-7c01-4b06-a0df-ebdf6ab9c24a","value":""},{"parameterId":"8cb8f430-d6c6-4b53-a529-eb3cfaa63d0e","value":""},{"parameterId":"0eadf821-34ff-49bf-8ba7-84f797359f43","value":""},{"parameterId":"ab9d7dc2-632c-4b35-89fc-c6d44752b52e","value":""},{"parameterId":"9c80ceb6-b8ed-47e8-ba07-cbdb602045d5","value":""},{"parameterId":"64a58022-5c7c-46e8-9d07-53c75a94c7dc","value":""}],"imageLinks":["","","","","","","","","","","","","","",""],"createdAt":"2026-01-28T18:14:54.762Z","updatedAt":"2026-01-28T18:47:28.278Z","images":[{"productId":"52ba6706-e6f2-4a1c-80ab-94e9e9918fba","imageFileId":"b5ded874-76d9-43a4-bd37-9605a0a358c7","assignedAt":"2026-01-28T18:14:55.095Z","imageFile":{"id":"b5ded874-76d9-43a4-bd37-9605a0a358c7","filename":"1769624094901-zx_pngjs_preview.png","filepath":"/uploads/products/KEYCHA999/1769624094901-zx_pngjs_preview.png","mimetype":"image/png","size":6783,"width":null,"height":null,"createdAt":"2026-01-28T18:14:54.949Z","updatedAt":"2026-01-28T18:14:54.949Z"}}],"catalogs":[{"productId":"52ba6706-e6f2-4a1c-80ab-94e9e9918fba","catalogId":"cad266e9-5a76-4ed3-8e49-a8c7b6bdfc10","assignedAt":"2026-01-28T18:14:55.296Z","catalog":{"id":"cad266e9-5a76-4ed3-8e49-a8c7b6bdfc10","name":"Mentios","description":"","isDefault":true,"defaultLanguageId":"EN","defaultPriceGroupId":"15ba906f-e2d1-4a0e-995f-67047a011ae5","createdAt":"2026-01-19T18:31:41.835Z","updatedAt":"2026-01-20T22:55:07.708Z","languageIds":["cmkhnn6lg0006o3c95op3jhq7","cmkhnn6lg0005o3c9gfxb0ykk","cmkhnn6lg0007o3c92punmjtg","PL","cmkmg9orm0007oac9ni5kehz6","cmkmg9orm0006oac98xheaprk","EN"],"priceG